nodes.text: 343.245/H5 was an Imperial commander in the Imperial Hammers Elite Armor Unit. During the Battle of Turak IV, this commander was in command of a team of two squads, Squad 5-Aurek and Squad 5-Cresh, that were sent to retrieve a downed, but still operational, repulsor tank, the Hammer 4:3. 343.245/H5 was also under orders to eliminate any opposition and bring the tank's crew safely home.
